s/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非響緊急場合雖然無乜用（對唔住我好廢） 但我地都應該唔會24hr 緊急場合嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f807d797744b552515ff8c34de72c93006bb96ad","tid":1468753,"uid":285312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"292432a4c961a7e093640b20e164e4f144c81d7f","tid":1468753,"uid":272892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:58:46.000Z","msg":"總之點都唔割！<br />\n香港人加油！永不放棄！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T21:14:27.000Z","msg":"唔割就一定嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我地唔割之餘都仲好需要改善<br />\n兄弟爬山有時都要一齊努力嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d054330c1d84577d7e91eefe9f8ddf75bfe0dca7","tid":1468753,"uid":272892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f807d797744b552515ff8c34de72c93006bb96ad","tid":1468753,"uid":285312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"292432a4c961a7e093640b20e164e4f144c81d7f","tid":1468753,"uid":272892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:58:46.000Z","msg":"總之點都唔割！<br />\n香港人加油！永不放棄！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T21:14:27.000Z","msg":"唔割就一定嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我地唔割之餘都仲好需要改善<br />\n兄弟爬山有時都要一齊努力嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T21:14:48.000Z","msg":"大家一齊加油！"},{"pid":"5f3a251bf4b39b9aaaa3453d0ea29b28e6fd69aa","tid":1468753,"uid":45007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"602844eae16bbe96340c77004429ec88670f8aa5","tid":1468753,"uid":285312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eb262096c69a90c2eb14391bd34e26398087e86","tid":1468753,"uid":45007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ce3eb9a